<small>RPA/financial-services adjacency, location, and Green Belt documentation gap.</small></a><a class="doc-link" href="automation-assurance-review.html"><strong>Automation Assurance Review</strong><small>A one-page working canvas for portfolio decisions and evidence.</small></a></div></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="section-inner"><div class="kicker">Public-source basis</div><h2>Research boundary</h2><p class="section-intro">Company-specific observations are grounded in public sources. Recommendations about USAA's internal automation portfolio are hypotheses for discovery, not assertions of private knowledge.</p><ol class="sources"><li><a href="https://newsroom.usaa360.com/about-us/learn-about-our-history-and-mission">USAA mission and history</a>.</li><li><a href="https://newsroom.usaa360.com/news/usaa-2025-annual-report-reflects-a-year-of-strength-service-and-commitment-to-members-1">USAA 2025 Annual Report release</a> and the linked report, including member-value, digital simplification, claims-processing, and First Notice of Loss examples.</li><li><a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-regulator-orders-usaa-federal-savings-bank-correct-unsafe-practices-2024-12-18/">Reuters reporting on the December 2024 OCC order</a>, used only as public operating context for the role's explicit risk-and-compliance mandate.</li><li><a href="https://www.usaajobs.com/job/-/-/1207/97567775696?p_sid=PcmdqGb&p_uid=aBEK7TXPkG&source=tmp_programmaticjobs&ss=paid&utm_campaign=other_other-priomarkets&utm_content=pj_board&utm_medium=jobad&utm_source=linkedin+slotted">USAA job posting: Director, Process Excellence - Process Automation</a>.</li></ol></div></section>
